PrecisAmendment to the DETERMINATION OF COUNTRY OF ORIGIN FOR THE PURPOSES OF MARKING GOODS (NAFTA COUNTRIES) REGULATIONS providing that Christmas trees, rose bushes and other bushes, shrubs and vines are not required to be marked with their country of origin unless they are imported in a container in which they ordinarily reach their ultimate purchaser.
